OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780653971
OL,3,CPolice issue warning after handing out
OL,4,Cincreased speeding fines due to TT
OL,5,Craces
OL,7,FPolice on the Isle of Man are urging
OL,8,Fdrivers to watch their speed - after
OL,9,Freporting an increase in speeding
OL,10,Ffines.
OL,12,FIt comes as thousands of motorcycle
OL,13,Fenthusiasts travel to see the TT
OL,14,Fraces, with many taking to the roads
OL,15,Fthemselves in between.
OL,17,FOfficers say they have already handed
OL,18,Fout more speeding fines than the 2025
OL,19,Fraces, with the 2026 festival not due
OL,20,Fto end until Saturday 6 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
