FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780653971
OL,3,CPolice issue warning after handing out
OL,4,Cincreased speeding fines due to TT
OL,5,Craces
OL,7,FPolice reported one instance of
OL,8,Fsomeone doing over 100mph in a 50mph
OL,9,Fzone.
OL,11,FInspector Elliot Butler said: "There
OL,12,Fwas somebody caught doing I think 188
OL,13,Fmiles per hour in a 50 zone, which is
OL,14,Fastronomical. We also had someone
OL,15,Fdoing double the speed limit in
OL,16,FOnchen, you know it's a village.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780653971
OL,3,CPolice issue warning after handing out
OL,4,Cincreased speeding fines due to TT
OL,5,Craces
OL,7,F"It's a small road, you're doing
OL,8,Fnearly double the speed limit through
OL,9,Fthere it's a 30 mile an hour speed
OL,10,Flimit and I believe they were doing
OL,11,Faround 60 miles per hour through it
OL,12,Fwhich is just unacceptable."
OL,14,FOne of the most famous corses of the
OL,15,FTT races is the Mountain Road, with
OL,16,Fmany motorcyclist travelling just to
OL,17,Ftake their own bike around the course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780653971
OL,3,CPolice issue warning after handing out
OL,4,Cincreased speeding fines due to TT
OL,5,Craces
OL,7,FSergeant Anthony Corlett said: "They
OL,8,Fcome over here to have fun and to have
OL,9,Fa good time and we want them to do
OL,10,Fthat. We just don't want people to
OL,11,Fover step that mark.
OL,13,F"We don't want to pick people up off
OL,14,Fthe road or attend a serious incident
OL,15,Fbecause a ripple effect from that is
OL,16,Ffar more than just dealing with those
OL,17,Fpeople at a scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780653971
OL,3,CPolice issue warning after handing out
OL,4,Cincreased speeding fines due to TT
OL,5,Craces
OL,7,F"It effects families, people over
OL,8,Fhere, locals, sometimes businesses,
OL,9,Ffarmers having their fences gone
OL,10,Fthrough all sorts of things. The
OL,11,Famount of people effected people don't
OL,12,Freally realise until it effects them,
OL,13,Fand we don't want it to effect them."
OL,15,FThe Isle of Man TT 2026 started on
OL,16,FMonday 25 May, and will end Saturday 6
OL,17,FJune 2026.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
